&amp;middot; A blog series with contributions from across the portfolio and linked contemporary policy debates http://www.urbantransformations.ox.ac.uk/news-and-debate/blog/
&amp;middot; A connections area that showcases all the partnerships that have been established through the research. There is an expanding selection of British, European and global organizations working in various capacities, such as research, industry and policy, to serve as a platform for partnerships, resource sharing and other opportunities. We hope this is proving a useful resource for those planning research and those wanting to engage with it http://www.urbantransformations.ox.ac.uk/connections/
&amp;middot; An events area where we post all events in the urban field -colour coded to show whether they are organised by UT, by a portfolio member or an external organisation http://www.urbantransformations.ox.ac.uk/events/
